OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud
OL,6,Fthickening to bring occasional rain,
OL,7,Fthis focused across Moray and western
OL,8,FAberdeenshire, with little expected to
OL,9,Fpenetrate to the east coast. Southerly
OL,10,Fcoastal winds initially fresh.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FEastern coastal areas
OL,13,Fmilder than Tuesday. Elsewhere
OL,14,Fsignificantly cooler. Rather cloudy
OL,15,Fmorning with a little light rain,
OL,16,Fmostly confined across far west.
OL,17,FMainly dry for the afternoon with
OL,18,Fbrighter spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
