OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FRain
OL,6,Fearly Thursday, clearing to brighter
OL,7,Fspells and showers for the afternoon.
OL,8,FFriday turning wet and windy with best
OL,9,Fof shelter in east. Showers Saturday,
OL,10,Fmore frequent in west.
